job.title: Sports Authority of India Coach Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for 320 Vacancies in India
job.body:
Total Vacancies:320

Name of the post:


 

Description:

The Sports Authority of India issued a total of 320 vacancies for the vacancies of Coach, Assistant Coach. The online application for these vacancies in India under the Sports Authority of India shall start from 20-04-2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 20-05-2021. Further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these vacancies in India is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for Sports Authority of India Coach Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • Available soon
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 20-04-2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 05-06-2021

Age limit criteria:

  • The Maximum Age Limit for Coach: 45 Years
  • The Maximum Age Limit for Assistant Coach: 40 Years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Sports Authority of India Coach Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per the 7th pay commission for the post of Coach is 95000/month
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed vacancies and educational qualification:

The vacancies in detail are given below. Check below that Sports Authority of India issued this notification for which vacancies.

 

How to apply for Sports Authority of India Coach Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of Sports Authority of India.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Coach.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
